{"tid":1359462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有線踢爆】元朗單野前一日警方已知情","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:52.000Z","uid":287903,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4a569c09f516251e4b2f748fa578323dd37f5eca","tid":1359462,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"大家好，P牌仔初黎報到，我明白最近大家都非常關注何妖，呢條友神憎鬼厭，攞到唔少attention。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但有兩單新聞大家可以煲大佢！！整圖spread開去係好重要！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新聞一：有線新聞刺針──【元朗衝突前 區議員已通知警方】</ins></strong><br />\n兩有兩位區議員證實，事發之前已經通知警方，仲要唔止一次！提咗警方幾次，點解可以一個鐘都無人出現？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/1110011325863830/UzpfSTE4NjA0MDcxNDkyMTMzODoxMTY1MDE3MjEwMzU3MDEy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F1110011325863830%2FUzpfSTE4NjA0MDcxNDkyMTMzODoxMTY1MDE3MjEwMzU3MDEy%2F&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTexSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=88add46c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/1110011325863830/UzpfSTE4NjA0MDcxNDkyMTMzODoxMTY1MDE3MjEwMzU3MDEy/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PcMuRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PcMuRv.jpg&h=3d5f6d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>新聞二：NOW──721警方上環驅散示威者未有示警橋上開槍</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356494&amp;fbclid=IwAR1w8-X2Kx2dMkyV6JWPXWixmjOD4tsRtrZMGgFt1X7zssfGeeFLZOFZrGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356494%26fbclid%3DIwAR1w8-X2Kx2dMkyV6JWPXWixmjOD4tsRtrZMGgFt1X7zssfGeeFLZOFZrGQ&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTexSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=69a5c0a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356494%26fbclid%3DIwAR1w8-X2Kx2dMkyV6JWPXWixmjOD4tsRtrZMGgFt1X7zssfGeeFLZOFZrGQ&h=4c73661a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/hom